snippet.textDisplay: Des Raj Lachkani - IS AWESOME!  New Life to Dhaadi Vaar.  Salim – Sulaiman mucho KUDOS for bringing them out and giving them the light.  The part that I didn't like was Namaste.  C'mon you can give more character to this.  A Vaar is a ballad sung, to energize armies.  These are war cries and songs of the Great.  You diluted to kukadu & namaste.  And the haath jod ke pyar baant le - its too sissy in lyrics & music.  This should have been hardrock heavy metal - that people loose their heads over.
